    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require all staff/resident interactions in care homes to be recorded",
        "additional_details": "I call for all interactions between care home staff and residents to be recorded, so that it is never possible for neglect and abuse to go unnoticed. This is especially important with everything that\u2019s going on with COVID, when it is harder for people to check on the care of our family.",
        "background": "With a lot of neglect and abuse in care homes. After experiencing issues with a family member in a care home I strongly suggest cameras in all areas of homes to stop the abuse of the elderly.",
